
1. Go to locale and run install.sh

   cd locale
   ./install.sh

2. (Optional) Open /etc/locale.alias and make sure si and
   si_LK entries are in alphabetically correct place.

3. Install the LKLUG OTF font in fonts/

4. Go to po/ directory and run si.sh

   cd po/
   ./si.sh

5. Recompile pango to your system using patches in
   rendering/pango.

6. Install gtk keyboard method in keyboard/gtk-im/

